message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you, which is valued at $10000. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it offers, I am extending an exclusive offer to you. For a limited time, you can acquire this product at a special price of $9500. This is an opportunity to save $500 while securing a high-quality item that matches your needs perfectly. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
